mias and cashews (140 g nuts in total) in this recipe.","Hemp seeds are from the same species as cannabis, but they don't have any psychoactive effects. On the contrary, they're exceptionally nutritious and a rich source of protein, omega fats and various vitamins and minerals.","Honey is not suitable for children under 1 year of age.","For an even smoother texture, place a nut milk bag over a large bowl. Pour mixture into nut milk bag and squeeze firmly to extract milk (however, you will lose some of the fibre).","You can store the Macadamia and hemp milk in the refrigerator for up to 5 days. The contents may settle, so be sure to give it a shake before using.","You can replace the fresh turmeric with 1½ tsp ground turmeric in this recipe, but the flavour will be earthier (the fresh turmeric has a fresher, more pleasant flavour)."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 10m","2 glasses"]}